Package: plot.igraph
Type: Package
Title: Extensions to iGraph for custom plots
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Author: Tom Kelly
Maintainer: Tom Kelly <tom.kelly@postgrad.otago.ac.nz>
Description: Functions to plot network or graph structures including customised colors, layout, states, arrows. Uses graphs functions as an extension of \code{\link[igraph]{igraph}}. Designed for plotting directed graphs.
License: GPL-3
